abstract: Bryce Molder wins Frys.com Open golf tournament in sudden-death playoff over Briny Baird; Ernie Els, one among a handful of players who had a share of the lead, finishes tied for fourth.
snippet: Ernie Els, who hasn’t won a tournament this year, saw progress at the Frys.com Open, which was won in a playoff by Bryce Molder.
lead_paragraph: Ernie Els, who hasn’t won a tournament this year, saw progress at the Frys.com Open, which was won in a playoff by Bryce Molder.

headline.main: Els Sees a Lot of Life Left in His Game
